{
  "stem": "1085.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First, messages from the Polish underground-- quasi-underground parliament.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The representatives of the four main political prewar parties-- Peasant Party, Nationalist Party, Socialist, and Christian Democratic Party, they formed a semi-- unofficial, underground parliament.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also, messages from the delegate of the government, who at that time was Cyryl Ratajski, and some individuals in the underground.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then in the meantime, the Jews got in touch with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They learned about my mission.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they asked the delegate to ask me, would I carry their messages on the same basis as the messages of other Polish political parties.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, he agreed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I agreed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I met them twice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One was-- identified himself as a socialist leader from Bund.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His identity is not doubted, because I described him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember his feature, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And many people knew him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had a beautiful face, mustachios, the-- a little to the-- up, like a Swedish 17th-century aristocracy, beautiful face, walking straight, rosy cheeks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He looked classical Polish nobleman, you know, estate owner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was in hiding, you know, under this-- he-- they told me he supposedly owned some little factories.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So he was well-to-do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "What was pathetic-- when he said he will go with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So he told me, for I will give you the sign when.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But in the meantime, don't shave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Prepare all this, so to not to be recognizable, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then we met, go to the ghetto and enter the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This was pathetic, that Polish nobleman, entering the ghetto, you know, humble, humiliated Jew-- [INAUDIBLE] Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You suddenly think, in  the whole 1,000-years history of Jewish persecution, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He played, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then he became a Jew of 2,000 years of the diaspora.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was Leon Finer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He died.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
